  fomor that was attempting to corrupt a Footscray meatworks; 
  spent his early operational career running Bone Gnawer 
  inner-Melbourne community-defence operations; rose to 
  Adren rank 2003 after the Geelong Pentex Subsidiary 
  Incident response; took the continental representative 
  role 2009 when his predecessor reached honourable retirement); ]

[ appearance(Tall, lean, the carriage of a man who has spent 
  fifty years moving through inner-Melbourne streets and 
